'''白藜芦醇'''（{{lang-en|resveratrol}}）是一种非[[黄酮|黄酮]]类的[[酚|酚]]类物质，屬於[[芪类化合物|芪类化合物]]的{{le|植物抗毒素|Phytoalexin}}、[[抗氧化劑|抗氧化劑]]。白藜芦醇是植物为了抵御[[細菌|細菌]]或[[真菌|真菌]]入侵而产生的物质<ref name="Ref5">{{cite web | vauthors = Higdon J, Drake VJ, Steward WP | title = Resveratrol | work = Micronutrient Information Center | publisher = Linus Pauling Institute, Oregon State University, Corvallis, OR | date = 2016 | url = http://lpi.oregonstate.edu/infocenter/phytochemicals/resveratrol/ | access-date = 2014-03-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130705035647/http://lpi.oregonstate.edu/infocenter/phytochemicals/resveratrol/ | archive-date = 2013-07-05 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Fremont|first1=Lucie|title=Biological Effects of Resveratrol|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0024320599004105|accessdate=6 June 2014|doi=10.1016/S0024-3205(99)00410-5|volume=66|issue=8|journal=Life Sciences|pages=663–673|pmid=10680575|date=January 2000|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924154630/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0024320599004105|dead-url=no}}</ref>。天然白藜芦醇的來源有[[葡萄|葡萄]]、[[藍莓|藍莓]]、[[樹莓|樹莓]]及[[桑葚|桑葚]]的果皮<ref name="Jansiski2013">{{cite journal | author = Jasiński M, Jasińska L, Ogrodowczyk M | title = Resveratrol in prostate diseases - a short review | journal = Cent European J Urol | volume = 66 | issue = 2 | pages = 144–9 | date = August 2013 | pmid = 24579014 | pmc = 3936154 | last2 = Jasińska | last3 = Ogrodowczyk | url = https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3936154/ | access-date = 2016-09-27 | archive-date = 2020-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200719054106/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3936154/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>以及[[花生|花生]]。

白藜芦醇目前常當作[[膳食補充劑|膳食補充劑]]。在一些動物實驗中，白藜芦醇對動物有幫助，但目前還沒有可靠的證據可以證實白藜芦醇對人體健康的幫助<ref name="pmid21698226">{{cite journal | vauthors = Vang O, Ahmad N, Baile CA, Baur JA, Brown K, Csiszar A, Das DK, Delmas D, Gottfried C, Lin HY, Ma QY, Mukhopadhyay P, Nalini N, Pezzuto JM, Richard T, Shukla Y, Surh YJ, Szekeres T, Szkudelski T, Walle T, Wu JM | title = What is new for an old molecule? Systematic review and recommendations on the use of resveratrol | journal = PLoS ONE | volume = 6 | issue = 6 | pages = e19881 | year = 2011 | pmid = 21698226 | pmc = 3116821 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0019881 | display-authors = 6 }}</ref>。

== 发现的历史 ==
* 早在1939年，日本人高冈从植物[[毛叶藜芦|毛叶藜芦]]（曾被当做[[白藜芦|白藜芦]]的[[变种|变种]]）的[[根茎|根茎]]提取了这种物质，命名Resveratrol。
* 1980年代，日本学者开始了解这种物质的抗[[氧化|氧化]]效果以及潛在的健康功效，但是并没有引起广泛注意。
* 1990年代，美国[[康涅狄格|康涅狄格]]的学者{{le|Dipak Kumar Das|Dipak Kumar Das}}認為[[葡萄酒|葡萄酒]]裡发现的白藜芦醇是造成[[法国悖论|法国悖论]]（法国人常食[[牛排|牛排]]、[[炸薯条|炸薯条]]等高[[胆固醇|胆固醇]]食品，但是其[[心血管病|心血管病]]的发病率只有美国的1/3）的原因<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://multivu.prnewswire.com/mnr/longevinex/42390/ |title=Resveratrol May Replace Aspirin As Heart Protector (Press release from Dr Dipak Das) |access-date=2016-09-30 |archive-date=2019-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212015816/http://multivu.prnewswire.com/mnr/longevinex/42390/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 2012年，[[康涅狄格大学|康涅狄格大学]]开除了畢業於印度的Calcutta University的Dipak K. Das教授，因为他在白藜芦醇的研究中造假。所以白藜芦醇的对于健康的实际作用，还缺乏确实的依据。关于红酒中的白藜芦醇Dipak K. Das总共发表了150篇文章；但是康涅狄格大学调查发现多于150篇是伪造数据的，其中包括他开除之前2012年1月的文章。实验室中的[[蛋白免疫印迹|蛋白免疫印迹]]（Western blot）數據有經過另外的修改。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Scientific Journals Notified Following Research Misconduct Investigation|url=https://today.uconn.edu/2012/01/scientific-journals-notified-following-research-misconduct-investigation/|access-date=2021-08-12|date=2012-01-11|work=UConn Today|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211106011014/https://today.uconn.edu/2012/01/scientific-journals-notified-following-research-misconduct-investigation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 功效 ==

===心臟疾病===
截至2014年，還沒有證據可以證實白藜芦醇對於[[心臟病|心臟病]]病患有所幫助<ref>{{cite journal | author = Tomé-Carneiro J, Gonzálvez M, Larrosa M, Yáñez-Gascón MJ, García-Almagro FJ, Ruiz-Ros JA, Tomás-Barberán FA, García-Conesa MT, Espín JC | title = Resveratrol in primary and secondary prevention of cardiovascular disease: a dietary and clinical perspective | journal = Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences | volume = 1290 | pages = 37–51 | date = Jul 2013 | pmid = 23855464 | doi = 10.1111/nyas.12150  | last2 = Gonzálvez | last3 = Larrosa | last4 = Yáñez-Gascón | last5 = García-Almagro | last6 = Ruiz-Ros | last7 = Tomás-Barberán | last8 = García-Conesa | last9 = Espín  | bibcode = 2013NYASA1290...37T }}</ref>。2014年一個中國的[[元分析|元分析]]研究許多以白藜芦醇為食品補充劑的研究，在每日劑量小於150 mg的相關研究中，對血壓沒有效果，若研究中的每天劑量大於150 mg，會降低收縮壓，但這也無法確認白藜芦醇的有效劑量<ref name=ResBP>{{cite journal | author = Liu Y, Ma W, Zhang P, He S, Huang D | title = Effect of resveratrol on blood pressure: A meta-analysis of randomized controlled trials | journal = Clinical Nutrition | volume = 34 | issue = 1 | pages = 27–34 | date = March 2014 | pmid = 24731650 | doi = 10.1016/j.clnu.2014.03.009 | last2 = Ma | last3 = Zhang | last4 = He | last5 = Huang }}</ref>。

===抗癌===
截至2014年，没有一致性良好的证据显示白藜芦醇在人類身上有抗癌作用<ref name="pmid24500760">{{cite journal | author = Carter LG, D'Orazio JA, Pearson KJ | title = Resveratrol and cancer: focus on in vivo evidence | journal = Endocr. Relat. Cancer | volume = 21 | issue = 3 | pages = R209–25 |date = June 2014  | pmid = 24500760 | pmc = 4013237 | doi = 10.1530/ERC-13-0171 | last2 = d'Orazio | last3 = Pearson }}</ref>。

===新陳代謝===
截至2014年，還沒有证据显示白藜芦醇對人類的[[新陳代謝|新陳代謝]]有幫助<ref name=Poul2013>{{cite journal | author = Poulsen MM, Jørgensen JO, Jessen N, Richelsen B, Pedersen SB | title = Resveratrol in metabolic health: an overview of the current evidence and perspectives | journal = Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences | volume = 1290 | pages = 74–82 | date = Jul 2013 | pmid = 23855468 | doi = 10.1111/nyas.12141 | last2 = Jørgensen | last3 = Jessen | last4 = Richelsen | last5 = Pedersen | bibcode = 2013NYASA1290...74P }}</ref><ref name=2014DiabetMeta>{{cite journal | author = Hausenblas HA, Schoulda JA, Smoliga JM | title = Resveratrol treatment as an adjunct to pharmacological management in type 2 diabetes mellitus-systematic review and meta-analysis | journal = Molecular nutrition & food research | volume = 59 | issue = 1 | pages = 147–59 | date = 19 August 2014 | pmid = 25138371 | doi=10.1002/mnfr.201400173| last2 = Schoulda | last3 = Smoliga }}</ref>。

===延长寿命===
2003年，Howitz及Sinclair 在《[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]》杂志上发表了白藜芦醇延长酵母菌的寿命的论文，随后的研究采用爬虫、果蝇及老鼠为样本，也有類似結果，

2011年，一个國際性的大型系統性研究认为白藜芦醇延长寿命的功效被夸大，實驗並未發現有抗衰老的效果<ref name="pmid21698226">{{cite journal | vauthors = Vang O, Ahmad N, Baile CA, Baur JA, Brown K, Csiszar A, Das DK, Delmas D, Gottfried C, Lin HY, Ma QY, Mukhopadhyay P, Nalini N, Pezzuto JM, Richard T, Shukla Y, Surh YJ, Szekeres T, Szkudelski T, Walle T, Wu JM | title = What is new for an old molecule? Systematic review and recommendations on the use of resveratrol | journal = PLoS ONE | volume = 6 | issue = 6 | pages = e19881 | year = 2011 | pmid = 21698226 | pmc = 3116821 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0019881 | display-authors = 6 }}</ref>

到2011年為止，還沒有足夠證據證實白藜芦醇可以延長人類的壽命<ref name=Fer2011>{{cite journal | author = Fernández AF, Fraga MF | title = The effects of the dietary polyphenol resveratrol on human healthy aging and lifespan | journal = Epigenetics | volume = 6 | issue = 7 | pages = 870–4 | date = Jul 2011 | pmid = 21613817 | doi = 10.4161/epi.6.7.16499 | last2 = Fraga }}</ref>。

